{"tid":1435514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以前係排華，依家中国係排港","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:32:05.000Z","uid":273218,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e799e82f2094e189971a3dacba3939f6ac55b58","tid":1435514,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講，過關北上多左個關只係搜香港人<br />\n我睇唔出香港人同新疆人有咩分別<br />\n本來我以前每星期都上去消費1，2次<br />\n同一般港豬上樣上去食好西飲西茶<br />\n621之後都無上過去消費<br />\n以前人人講排華<br />\n依家上面罷明係排港<br />\n有骨氣既都應該抵制唔再去中国<br />\n本來佔中後都欺騙左自己，仍然上去<br />\n621後已過唔到自己果關，同上面完全割席"},{"pid":"d9576607d79240825cd2241dd079cda21e6e7b39","tid":1435514,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"因為呢個主張，同幾個撐共北上港豬絕左交"},{"pid":"c8ba0375f7a029cae7f609c726ea707a490a1ade","tid":1435514,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"揮國旗，燒黨旗！！！大家各有各做，分化敵人內部！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433273\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433273</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"441bfccf15c5ccbee27699e0382ef139eb2b455f","tid":1435514,"uid":126835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"係撚排港咩 係佢地自悲咋屌<br />\n係都我地排蝗啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5f63e49eaaa59d1daab917ac063e6b9e663ca6","tid":1435514,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"上去消費都算<br />\n唔需要話港獨抵打，打多幾下<br />\n又話要護旗<br />\n微信見到我即刪<br />\n刪左好多人"},{"pid":"800e34bc5871d2e716524ba7ae02a9619f0fd409","tid":1435514,"uid":52577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上去食元素表<br />\n怪得邊個？"},{"pid":"0dec95a19fb731683